quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  42,23,"Ko Й—uum woni ko Allah wewlinirta jiyaaЙ“e makko gooЕ‹Й—iiЙ“e Й“en, Й“e ngolli golle moЖґЖґe. Maaku: "Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di e Й—um, si wonaa tun giggol enЙ—am Й—am". Kala paggitiiЙ—o moЖґЖґere, Min Й“eydanay mo moЖґЖґere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo, mantoowo."
  42,24,"Kaa Й“e mbi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notatno e Й“ernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol makko ngol. Pellet, ko O gannduЙ—o gunndooji Й“erЙ—e Й—een."
  42,25,"Ko KaЕ‹ko woni jaЙ“anoowo jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“een tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bonЙ—i Й—in, e hoore Himo anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gooЕ‹Й—inЙ“e Й“een, Й“e ngolli moЖґЖґuЙ—i, O Й“eydana Й“e e Й“ural makko ngal. HeeferЙ“e Й“en non, hino woodani Й“e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e."
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaГ±Г±anno jiyaaЙ“e Makko Й“een [fof] arsike, pellet, Й“e bewayno ka leydi; kono Homo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O kummpitiiЙ—o, yioowo jeyyaaЙ“e makko Й“een."
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo toЙ“o ngoon Й“aawo Й“e taЖґaade, O saaka yurmeende makko nden. Ko KaЕ‹ko kadi woni GiЙ—o, jettiniiЙ—o On."
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—iin: tagugol kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin, e ruugayЙ—i Й—i O saaki Й—in hakkunde majji. KaЕ‹ko e fii mooЙ“indiroygol Й“e ngool, si O haajii, ko O kattanЙ—o."
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—een faggitii kon. Himo ya'afoo noon, ko Й—uuЙ—i."
  42,31,"OOn wonaani laawotooЙ“e ka leydi ; alanaa on ga Allah, giЙ—o, wanaa ballo."